# BODYiQ Mobile Conventions

## Structure
- `app/` — Expo Router screens: `(auth)/`, `(onboarding)/`, `(tabs)/`
- `src/components/` — UI primitives + features
- `src/theme/` — tokens; `src/lib/` — supabase, query client
- `src/hooks/`, `src/services/`, `src/types/`

## Styling
Use NativeWind + tokens from `src/theme/tokens.ts`. Default to dark surfaces, white text, copper accents.

## Patterns
- Functional components; extract hooks for data fetching
- TanStack Query for Supabase reads/writes; Zustand for onboarding wizard state
- Zod schemas colocated in `src/types/`
- Simplicity default: simplest UX path is always the default

## Auth flow
Unauthenticated → `(auth)/`; post-login without intake → `(onboarding)/`; complete → `(tabs)/`.

## Examples
```tsx
// ✅ Use Screen wrapper + theme tokens
<Screen><Button variant="primary">Continue</Button></Screen>

// ❌ Hardcode colors
<View style={{ backgroundColor: '#C37663' }} />
```
